title: Soros and Schwab Skip Davos
author: VD
content_html:
Something is up…

It could be they caught word of the hypothetical Joint Winter Offensive starting next week. Or it could be the vaxx. Or it could be something else. Regardless, two of Clown World’s leading clowns skipping its annual grand circus is certainly unexpected.
